OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780387618
OL,3,CDean Harrison secures first TT
OL,4,CSuperbike victory in 'dominant' display
OL,6,FDean Harrison claimed a dominant
OL,7,Fvictory in the opening Superbike race
OL,8,Fat the Isle of Man TT.
OL,10,FThe Honda Racing UK rider finished
OL,11,F15.5 seconds ahead of runner-up Peter
OL,12,FHickman, while Michael Dunlop secured
OL,13,Fthird place.
OL,15,FSetting the fastest lap of the race at
OL,16,Fan incredible 134.892mph, the win
OL,17,Fmarks Harrison's sixth TT victory.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
