PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780387618
OL,3,CDean Harrison secures first TT
OL,4,CSuperbike victory in 'dominant' display
OL,6,FThe milestone draws him level with
OL,7,Ficonic motorsport names Jimmy Guthrie,
OL,8,FGeoff Duke, John Surtees, Jim Redman,
OL,9,Fand sidecar passenger Chas Birks.
OL,11,FHarrison, who is from Bradford,
OL,12,Fasserted his authority early on
OL,13,FSunday, 31 May, opening up a 4.8-
OL,14,Fsecond advantage over Dunlop by the
OL,15,Ftime he reached Glen Helen on the
OL,16,Fopening lap.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780387618
OL,3,CDean Harrison secures first TT
OL,4,CSuperbike victory in 'dominant' display
OL,6,FHe continually extended his lead
OL,7,Facross the Mountain Course, pushing
OL,8,Fthe gap over the 30-second mark by the
OL,9,Fend of lap four. Behind the leader,
OL,10,Fthe battle was on for the remaining
OL,11,Fpodium spots.
OL,13,FHickman, competing for Monster Energy
OL,14,FBMW Motorrad by 8TEN Racing on his
OL,15,Fcomeback from injury, traded positions
OL,16,Fwith Dunlop for the majority of the
OL,17,Fsix-lap race.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
