OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780387618
OL,3,CDean Harrison secures first TT
OL,4,CSuperbike victory in 'dominant' display
OL,6,FA quick pit stop helped Hickman edge
OL,7,Fahead, and a quick final lap of
OL,8,F134.587mph sealed second place. Dunlop
OL,9,Ffinished a further 12.4 seconds behind
OL,10,Fin third on his MD Racing Honda.
OL,12,FFurther down the field, Josh Brookes
OL,13,Fsecured fourth place for DAO Racing
OL,14,FHonda, pulling 19.5 seconds clear of
OL,15,Froad racing veteran John McGuinness.
OL,17,FMcGuinness delighted the crowds in
OL,18,Ffifth place, running a special
OL,19,Fthrowback livery on his Honda Racing
OL,20,FUK machine to commemorate his very
OL,21,Ffirst TT appearance in 1996.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
